Before Virtual server: 
Scaling the server is Horizontal Scaling and Sacling the resources on the existing server is Vertical Scaling.


In the kubernetes:

Scaling Cluster Infra:
A. Scaling the node is horizontal
B. Scaling the resources on the node is vertical


Scaling Workloads:
A. Scaling the pod is horizontal pod autoscaler
B. Scaling the resources on the pod is vertical pod autoscaler


